  <p class="">Unsurprisingly, this process has taken a digital turn. There are some perks to going digital:</p><ol data-rte-list="default"><li><p class=""><strong>The turnaround time is instant.</strong> Whether you are sending a signature from one end of the office to another, or sending it off to another continent, the communication tools we can apply in the 21st century allows us to have instant communication.</p></li><li><p class=""><strong>Less clutter. </strong>Physically, at least. E-filing makes it easy for employees to organize and update files where needed.</p></li><li><p class=""><strong>Less room for human error. </strong>Thanks to handy programs like Excel and Grammarly, there is a lower chance of making clerical mistakes in calculations and spelling in your documents. </p></li></ol>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
