  <h3>Ways Merlin Shredding has reduced their footprint</h3><p class="">As many of you know, our environmental impact here at Merlin is very important to us. So we'd also like to share some of the extra of the ways we reduce our footprint! Merlin Shredding is completely paperless and our offices are made completely out of recycled materials. We’ve made upgrades to our shredding trucks such as switches that lower the ide to save fuel, and the use of eco-friendly oils and lubricants. And last but not least helping other companies reduce their footprint through recycling programs. You can take a look at all our environmental efforts<a href="https://www.merlinshredding.com/environmental-impact"><span> here on our website</span></a> and see for yourself why Merlin Shredding is the best fit for all your shredding needs.</p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/1628539979156-1KY78CMVBAJOP3MHCYU7/AdobeStock_318383922.jpeg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1000"><media:title type="plain">Paper Waste In Canada And How Shredding Can Help Reduce It</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>3 Strategies To Lower Risk In Hybrid Work Environments</title><dc:creator>Guest User</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 15 Jul 2022 13:58:19 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.merlinshredding.com/blog/3-strategies-for-hybrid-model-security-protection</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e:6047f052f7b2925db6ce25fd:62c4adc4d6dbb04e88d5a0cf</guid><description><![CDATA[Hybrid models are here to stay. We’ve included 3 strategies to ensure 
information remains safe in the shifting work landscape.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure class="
