                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1010x720" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=1000w" width="1010" height="720" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6047e4c6dfc6544ed63c758e/8d2b5fbc-2dc0-4474-8f04-aa9c44f0c2c2/shutterstock4613557242DQ2_0.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h2>2. Make sure you are on a trusted network and wifi.</h2><p class="">Once you’ve realized you need to order something, it can be tempting to order as fast as possible so you don’t forget to! But, before you start filling in your personal information, make sure you check that you are on a trusted shopping site and the right wifi. To check if the site is safe, look for a little padlock symbol in the url bar. Then, make sure you are on a private wifi connection. Once you have checked both, you are good to move forward with entering your private information!</p><h2>3. Double check what you click. </h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
