        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Now more than ever, identity theft is rising and data storage allowing larger amounts of information to be stored on one source means shredding is an essential activity in our workplaces.</p><p class="">Some of these additional threats include ID badges, laptops and computer hard drives, cellphones, and other devices. <br><br>With increased storage, no one can simply delete information and assume the data cannot be retrieved with advanced technology.   Grinding or shredding technology completely removes the data layering and coding sequences from all digital sources, reducing the information to powder.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
