  <h3>3. Formal Reporting Mechanisms</h3><p class="">Create a formal reporting mechanism, whether an anonymous form or a different method, that allows individuals to come forward in a way that ensures their anonymity and confidentiality. </p><p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
